<!--
name: ansible deploy from git
description: Deploy source code from git repo to a group of webservers
moreinfo: http://ansible.cc/docs/examples.html#deploying-from-source-control
keywords: cap, capistrano, fabric, git, deploy
author: Folks at Ansible
